Dahlman Hires Robert Meier of Gleacher as Head of Equity Sales

-- B y   J e f f   K e a r n s
-- 
2011-12-13T19:09:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-13/dahlman-hires-robert-meier-of-gleacher-as-head-of-equity-sales.html
Dahlman Rose & Co., the New York-
based investment bank specializing in transportation, energy and
commodity companies, hired Robert Meier of Gleacher & Co. as
head of equity sales and trading.  Meier, 48, oversaw equity sales, trading and research at
Gleacher and prior to joining that firm was co-head of equities
at Cowen Group Inc., according to a statement from the firm. He
will report to Chief Executive Officer Kim Fennebresque.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Kearns in New York at 
 jkearns3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nick Baker at 
 nbaker7@bloomberg.net  